{
  "texts": [
    "However, this comes at the cost of significant battery depletion (see Sec.",
    "5.2.2), QoE (see Sec.",
    "5.2.3) and end-task accuracy (see Sec. 5.4).",
    "Therefore, we envision that the future of LLM execution can be collaborative and cross-device at the edge [57,81].",
    "To this direction, we test to see the viability of offloading the DNN execution to a local edge device, which might be a dedicated accelerator (e.g., an Edge-AI Hub) or another edge device (e.g., a Smart TV or a high-end router)."
  ]
